Module Code: MOD-STAFF
Priority: Critical MVP
Version: 1.0
Frontend: Flutter + BLoC
Backend: NestJS
Dependencies: Authentication Module, Audit Module, Notification Module, Device Management Module

⸻

1. Module Purpose

The Staff & RBAC (Role-Based Access Control) Module governs who can access what within the Jewellery ERP system.

This module is responsible for:

* Staff Management
* User Creation
* Role Management
* Permission Management
* Device Approval
* Session Monitoring
* Staff Activity Tracking
* Login History
* Access Control Enforcement
* Security Governance

All modules depend on this module.

