7. Core Business Rules

BR-RBAC-001

Every user must have at least one role.

BR-RBAC-002

Owner account cannot be deleted.

BR-RBAC-003

Permission changes require audit logs.

BR-RBAC-004

Device approval requires Owner permission.

BR-RBAC-005

Session termination available only to Owner.

BR-RBAC-006

Permission checks executed on backend and frontend.

BR-RBAC-007

Every API must validate permissions.

BR-RBAC-008

Permission denial must be logged.

